headline: Brookfield Renewable (BEP) Surges 5.1%: Is This an Indication of Further Gains?
summary: Brookfield Renewable (BEP) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock suggests that there could be more strength down the road.

headline: Pinnacle West Capital to Post Q3 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
